  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9b/9bfebc82456ef092e891263d0ed79dd6.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Image courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\" data-size=\"3600x2100\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9b/9bfebc82456ef092e891263d0ed79dd6.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9b/9bfebc82456ef092e891263d0ed79dd6.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9b/9bfebc82456ef092e891263d0ed79dd6.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9b/9bfebc82456ef092e891263d0ed79dd6.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Image courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\" alt=\"Image courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThe need for the burgeoning \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/218076/adu\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eADU\u003c/a\u003e market in the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/81596/southern-california\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSouthern California\u003c/a\u003e market is commanding a closer look. As such, here’s an interesting project from Michael Matthews Studio, which was just named a Citation Award winner at the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/bustler/10231/los-angeles-best-new-and-future-projects-honored-at-the-2024-aia-la-design-awards\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAIA Los Angeles Design Awards\u003c/a\u003e in December.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c5e5da137bf987c1084f9cd04e1093b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x680\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c5e5da137bf987c1084f9cd04e1093b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c5e5da137bf987c1084f9cd04e1093b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c5e5da137bf987c1084f9cd04e1093b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c5e5da137bf987c1084f9cd04e1093b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWorking for a relocated client on a sloping 0.6-acre parcel in the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/54693/san-diego\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSan Diego\u003c/a\u003e area, Matthews’ Barrel Cactus ADU is a 1-bed/1-bath 1,050-square-foot design attached to a one-story midcentury modern home. As the name suggests, barrel-vaulted ceilings and a reference to endemic Saguaro Cactus plants are its defining characteristics. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f0/f0ef284e60bce0ef814243b4103b2e1c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x579\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f0/f0ef284e60bce0ef814243b4103b2e1c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f0/f0ef284e60bce0ef814243b4103b2e1c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f0/f0ef284e60bce0ef814243b4103b2e1c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/f0/f0ef284e60bce0ef814243b4103b2e1c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eA \u0026#34;contemporary response” then forms via a rheumatic response between the glass-fiber reinforced roofline and bioretentive cactus planters, allowing for a high thermal mass. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9f/9f2862da960f9a48c9d9ead4fd1abf7f.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x702\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9f/9f2862da960f9a48c9d9ead4fd1abf7f.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9f/9f2862da960f9a48c9d9ead4fd1abf7f.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9f/9f2862da960f9a48c9d9ead4fd1abf7f.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/9f/9f2862da960f9a48c9d9ead4fd1abf7f.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe introduction of clerestory windows and the possibility of deep overhangs provide the space with further increases in natural light and a reduction in solar gain. The design also features on-site stormwater retention. \u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/gallery/150463003/1/michael-matthews-studio-shares-details-of-award-winning-barrel-cactus-adu\" title=\"Image courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e1/e182778fffb56c4aee553fdeea2f49bb.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=80\u0026amp;h=80 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e1/e182778fffb56c4aee553fdeea2f49bb.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=80\u0026amp;h=80\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e1/e182778fffb56c4aee553fdeea2f49bb.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=80\u0026amp;h=80\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/e1/e182778fffb56c4aee553fdeea2f49bb.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=80\u0026amp;h=80\" title=\"Image courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\" alt=\"Image courtesy Michael Matthews Studio\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/gallery/150463003/2/mic